# tests/.env — local-only credentials for integration tests.
#
# Copy to tests/.env (gitignored) and fill in the values. The
# tests/common package's init walks up from its source dir to this
# file on first import and propagates the keys below into the test
# process env. Host-exported values always win — exporting a key in
# your shell overrides whatever this file holds.
#
# Whitelisted keys (anything else in this file is ignored):
#   GEMINI_API_KEY        — Google AI Studio key for the Gemini reviewer.
#   GEMINI_REVIEW_MODEL   — model id, e.g. gemini-2.5-flash. Empty = default.
#   EMBEDDINGS_API_KEY    — provider API key for the embedding worker.
#   EMBEDDINGS_PROVIDER   — gemini | openai | stub | none.
#   EMBEDDINGS_MODEL      — model id (e.g. text-embedding-004 for gemini).

GEMINI_API_KEY=
GEMINI_REVIEW_MODEL=
EMBEDDINGS_API_KEY=
EMBEDDINGS_PROVIDER=
EMBEDDINGS_MODEL=
